6
00:02:37,440 --> 00:02:38,440
Miss.

7
00:02:39,840 --> 00:02:42,360
Do you ride the
Route 45 bus often?

8
00:02:48,400 --> 00:02:52,280
Has anyone ever taken
advantage of you on the bus?

9
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,360
Take advantage of me?

10
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:05,080
Was there a man who
wanted to touch you?

11
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:08,496
- Take advantage, violate, and harass you?
- What are you doing?

12
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,776
- What's wrong with you?
- Was there? Miss, please tell me.

13
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,360
- Sir!
- Let go of me! Was there?

14
00:03:12,440 --> 00:03:13,520
That person is sick!

15
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:16,040
- Stop it or I'll call the police!
- Miss!

16
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,600
I'm not sick.

17
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:19,600
Hello? I'm calling the police.

18
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,880
HONGQIANG CABLE FACTORY
TO XUEYE SOUTH ROAD

19
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,120
How many times is this?

20
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,880
If I remember correctly, this
is the third time, right?

21
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:35,080
Please make sure we don't
get any more complaints

22
00:03:35,160 --> 00:03:36,280
that make us send officers.

23
00:03:36,360 --> 00:03:38,160
Can we not do this again?

24
00:03:38,720 --> 00:03:40,320
I understand how you feel.

25
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,240
But your investigation

26
00:03:42,320 --> 00:03:46,080
has already caused significant disruption
to Route 45 bus drivers and passengers.

27
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:47,680
Can you be more careful?

28
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,080
Who am I disturbing?

29
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,200
How did I disturb them?

30
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:54,040
If you didn't, would I be here?

31
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,560
Please trust the police.

32
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,480
Stop!

33
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,240
- Officer.
- What are you doing?

34
00:04:01,880 --> 00:04:04,400
Please calm down.

35
00:04:04,480 --> 00:04:05,480
Listen to me.

36
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:08,280
Look at her.

37
00:04:09,200 --> 00:04:11,760
Please try to understand.

38
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:14,200
I'm here.

39
00:04:14,280 --> 00:04:15,880
I won't let her
cause trouble. Relax.

40
00:04:17,840 --> 00:04:18,840
Mr. Wang.

41
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:21,240
I can understand how you feel.

42
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:24,040
I have kids too.

43
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,200
But the case is closed.

44
00:04:27,279 --> 00:04:29,360
What are you aiming
for by keeping this up?

45
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:33,880
Take my advice.

46
00:04:33,960 --> 00:04:35,400
Don't do it again.

47
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:37,120
Go home and talk to her.

48
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:39,720
There won't be the next time.

49
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,760
I'm sorry for the trouble.

50
00:04:42,240 --> 00:04:43,240
Okay.

51
00:04:43,280 --> 00:04:44,120
You guys go ahead.

52
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,200
Thank you.

53
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:46,800
Thank you.

54
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:48,640
Let's go.

55
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:52,600
Mr. Wang.

56
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:54,040
Take her home.
Don't stand there.

57
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,200
They couldn't find any evidence.

58
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,400
They won't let us search either.

59
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:28,040
Ambulance!

60
00:06:28,680 --> 00:06:31,440
Where's the ambulance?

61
00:07:07,960 --> 00:07:09,400
His wound has been treated.

62
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,160
It's not that serious.

63
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,360
He just lost a lot of blood.

64
00:07:12,440 --> 00:07:13,360
He needs to stay.

65
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,440
Xiaolu.

66
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:16,200
- Take them to the inpatient ward.
- Okay.

67
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,800
Come with me.

68
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:18,880
Thank you.

69
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,800
Hold on.

70
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:24,960
Are you Xiao Heyun?

71
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,840
I need to talk to you right now.

72
00:07:26,920 --> 00:07:29,200
How did you know there
was a bomb on the bus?

73
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,560
Tell me.

74
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:31,880
Officer.

75
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,280
He lost a lot of blood.

76
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,520
He needs to rest.

77
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,320
You can ask him later.

78
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:37,600
I won't take much of his time.

79
00:07:37,640 --> 00:07:39,600
- I just have two questions.
- This is a hospital.

80
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,880
Ms. Du is on the phone.

81
00:07:40,960 --> 00:07:42,280
Xiaolu, take them to the ward.

82
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:43,360
Okay.

83
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,520
Come on, follow me.

84
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,600
Ms. Du.

85
00:07:50,640 --> 00:07:52,760
The one who called the police
is very important to us.

86
00:07:52,840 --> 00:07:53,840
Got it.

87
00:07:54,440 --> 00:07:56,760
Keep me updated on
Mr. Zhang's situation.

88
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:58,360
I'll stay at the hospital.

89
00:08:12,640 --> 00:08:13,640
Ms. Du.

90
00:08:15,480 --> 00:08:17,120
Those two just won't talk.

91
00:08:17,200 --> 00:08:18,320
They refuse to cooperate.

92
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:23,320
Leave them be for a while.

93
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:26,080
We'll interrogate them
after we know more.

94
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:36,080
RESUSCITATION BAY (SECTOR A)

95
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:45,039
RESUSCITATION BAY (SECTOR A)

